6
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:41,340
[Episode 3]

7
00:00:42,060 --> 00:00:42,380
Brother,

8
00:00:42,820 --> 00:00:44,100
am I the closest person to you?

9
00:00:45,420 --> 00:00:46,500
Of course.

10
00:00:48,380 --> 00:00:49,140
Then tell me

11
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:50,620
