12
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:54,580
Don't trust that guy's nonsense.

13
00:00:55,060 --> 00:00:55,700
Also,

14
00:00:56,860 --> 00:00:57,460
from now on,

15
00:00:58,380 --> 00:00:59,340
keep your distance from him.

16
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:03,460
Why is he so angry?

17
00:01:05,100 --> 00:01:05,580
Brother,

18
00:01:05,900 --> 00:01:07,060
