do you?

19
00:01:09,740 --> 00:01:11,140
Go back to school.

20
00:01:11,580 --> 00:01:12,180
Or else,

21
00:01:12,860 --> 00:01:14,860
I won't buy you red bean cakes
for a month.

22
00:01:16,060 --> 00:01:17,100
It's not a big issue.

23
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:18,860
As long as you're alive and well

24
00:01:19,180 --> 00:01:20,340
and we can stay together.

25
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:29,740
I'm heading back to the art school.

26
00:01:32,260 --> 00:01:33,420
Brother, you have to be okay.

27
00:01:33,740 --> 00:01:34,540
No need to take me there.

28
00:01:46,660 --> 00:01:48,540
This is absurd.

29
00:01:48,990 --> 00:01:56,620
[Lin Yueniang, Lin Yucheng, Lin Chu]

30
00:01:56,620 --> 00:01:57,420
Qingming,

31
00:01:59,620 --> 00:02:00,500
I heard

32
00:02:00,500 --> 00:02:02,940
you sent out Shaozi
to track down Cao Fang.

33
00:02:03,060 --> 00:02:03,420
Yes.

34
00:02:04,220 --> 00:02:05,460
I must capture Cao Fang.

35
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:07,340
Whether the Lin family's annihilation
was a mistake

36
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:09,300
and who killed Jingzhe,

37
00:02:09,900 --> 00:02:10,980
I must find out the truth.

38
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:19,140
Bingtang Hulu.

39
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:21,660
Secret trouble?

40
00:02:23,180 --> 00:02:25,380
What illness does he have, exactly?

41
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,860
Centurial miracle remedy.

42
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:28,380
Passed down for generations.

43
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:30,460
Cure kidney deficiency
and tonify the kidney.

44
00:02:30,740 --> 00:02:33,540
Specifically for men's secret trouble.

45
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:35,820
Doctor!

46
00:02:35,820 --> 00:02:37,220
[Centurial Miracle Remedy]

47
00:02:37,220 --> 00:02:38,100
Does your medicine

48
00:02:38,100 --> 00:02:39,380
really work as you say?

49
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:40,540
Absolutely.

50
00:02:40,860 --> 00:02:42,660
It's a secret formula passed down
for over a century.

51
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:44,220
Just a few doses will do.

52
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,380
[Curing kidney deficiency,
tonifying the kidney]

53
00:02:46,380 --> 00:02:48,420
So, it'll all be cured after taking it?

54
00:02:48,460 --> 00:02:49,780
Definitely.

55
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:50,420
Trust me.

56
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:51,820
How much for one dose?

57
00:02:52,220 --> 00:02:53,060
Twenty wen a dose.

58
00:02:53,860 --> 00:02:54,820
Three doses should be enough.

59
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:56,260
Ten doses, please.

60
00:02:56,460 --> 00:02:56,820
OK.

61
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:03,740
Is it hot?

62
00:03:03,940 --> 00:03:04,460
No.

63
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:05,340
Brother,

64
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:06,300
drink up.

65
00:03:06,540 --> 00:03:08,140
I specially
made this chicken soup for you.

66
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:09,140
It's nutritious.

67
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:10,820
Looks good.

68
00:03:14,180 --> 00:03:14,740
Enough,

69
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:15,700
let me taste it first.

70
00:03:22,180 --> 00:03:22,700
Is it good?

71
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:24,420
Tasty.

72
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:25,740
Have a try.

73
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:26,620
No.

74
00:03:26,620 --> 00:03:27,540
I made it especially for you.

75
00:03:27,540 --> 00:03:27,980
Have some more.

76
00:03:29,900 --> 00:03:30,500
Sure.

77
00:03:30,980 --> 00:03:32,500
My sister made this for me.

78
00:03:32,620 --> 00:03:33,060
I'll surely have more.

79
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:43,940
Brother,

80
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:46,540
what happened to you?

81
00:04:54,740 --> 00:04:55,820
Are you okay?

82
00:05:00,740 --> 00:05:01,260
Brother,

83
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:03,780
