85
00:05:27,690 --> 00:05:30,320
♪Love and hatred intertwined♪

86
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,900
♪My sorrow overwhelmed♪

87
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:34,300
Brother.

88
